                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-75-off377 t17850914-75-cd378"></join> last, ten pounds weight of beef, value 3 s. two fowls, value 2 s. two pounds weight of cheese, value 6 d. and one rush basket, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850914-75-victim849" type="victimName">
                     Michael 
                     Heathcote
                  <interp inst="t17850914-75-victim849" type="surname" value="Heathcote"></interp>
